* Female mask, Muromachi period
* Sacred bell
* Wooden seated monk statue, Muromachi period
* Spring water of Tamanoi (historic site)

=== Transportation ===
* {{jalink|i-Bus|Q11223722}}: Kisogawa/Kitagata course, get off at "Kamo Shrine North" stop.
* About 5 minutes on foot from {{jalink|Tamanoi Station|Q7680699}} on the {{jalink|Meitetsu Bisai Line|Q901005|Bisai Line}} of {{jalink|Nagoya Railroad|Q30850|Meitetsu}}.

