=== Cultural properties ===
=== Aichi Prefecture designated tangible cultural property ===
* Kishin mask (craft)

=== Ichinomiya City designated tangible cultural properties ===
* Old shrine gate (building)
* Noh masks (one male and one female face) (sculpture)
* Two swords (craft)
* Ancient mirror (craft)
* Ancient mirror (chrysanthemum-scatter twin-sparrow mirror)
* Ancient mirror (auspicious-flower butterfly twin-phoenix mirror)
* Ancient mirror (auspicious-flower twin-phoenix octagonal mirror)
* Two kishin masks, Muromachi period
* Female mask, Muromachi period
* Sacred bell
* Wooden seated monk statue, Muromachi period
* Spring water of Tamanoi (historic site)

=== Transportation ===
* {{ill|lt=i-Bus|Q11223722|qid=Q11223722|1=I-Bus}}: Kisogawa/Kitagata course, get off at "Kamo Shrine North" stop.
* About 5 minutes on foot from {{ill|lt=Tamanoi Station|Q7680699|qid=Q7680699|1=Tamanoi Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Meitetsu Bisai Line|Q901005|qid=Q901005|lt=Bisai Line|1=Meitetsu Bisai Line}} of {{ill|lt=Nagoya Railroad|Q30850|qid=Q30850|lt=Meitetsu|1=Meitetsu}}.

